data.description: Three-bedroom two-bathroom home with expansive fenced in private backyard, making a safe yard for pets and family to enjoy the outdoors. Convenient highway access making daily commute a breeze.  Recently finished lower-level family room and bedroom. Some fresh paint and enjoy lots of natural light through the large windows in living room. There is room for further personalization. Current owners had used the porch as primary bedroom.
